<strong>Beeso</strong> ({{lang-en|Money}}) waa shey ka samaysan [[bir]], [[shilin]]ka, iyo [[warqad]] leh astaamo iyo calaamado kala duwan taas oo [[dad]]ku isla garteen in wax lagu kala iibsado. Beesadu waa shey miisaan yar oo lagu qiimeeyo qadarka alaab, badeecad, guri, dhul iyo waxyaabo kale leeyihiin.

Hadaba [[duni|dunida maanta]] waxaa jira [[tiro]] badan oo lacag ah, wadan kasta wuxuu leeyahay beeso u gaar ah, taasi oo qiimaheedu kala sareeyo isla markaana ka sameeysan [[shilin|shilimaan]] iyo [[warqad]]o. 

Guud ahaan beesadu waa labo nooc: mid shilin ah iyo mid warqad ka sameeysan. Shilimaantu waa qadarka ugu qiimaha hooseeya lacagta wadan leeyahay, inta badana waxa ka soo bilaabmaan [[hal|hal senti]], [[shan|shan senti]], [[toban|toban senti]], [[konton|konton senti]] iyo [[boqol|boqol senti]].

Boqolka senti wixii ka sareeya waxaa la isticmaalaa warqad taas oo ka bilaabanta [[kow]] ilaa [[milyan|malaayiin]]. Laakiin inta badan, lacagta dunida waxaa ugu sareeysa warqad [[kun|shan kun]] ah.

= Taariikhda Beesada =
Inkasto aanan la hubin, waxaa la sheegaa in sheeyo u eeg [[shilin]]ka la isticmaali jirey [[sanad|100,000 sano]] ka hor. Laakiin waxaa la hubaa in lacagtii ugu horeeysay ay sameeyeen ganacsatadii hore ee [[beer]]aleyda ahayd ee [[ilbaxnimo]]dii [[Mesobotaamiya]] (Mesopotamia) [[wakhti]] hada laga joogo [[sanad|3,000 sano]] Ciise hortiis. 

Sidoo kale, lacagta bocoolsha (shell money) wakhtiyo hore ayaa laga isticmaali jirey [[qaarad]] [[Afrika]], [[Aasiya]], [[Ameerika]] iyo Ustareeliya. 

Shilinka shaanbadeysan ee astaamaha iyo calaamadaha leh, kaas oo ka samaysan [[dahab]] iyo [[naxaas]], waxaa la alifey intii u dhaxaysay [[sanad|650 ilaa 600]] ciise hortiis.

